{"tid":2213184,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陳彥霖逝世一年 網民知專外發起悼念會 警持槍嚴密戒備","createTime":"2020-09-22T10:45:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T12:55:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"3894c11268d42ab4ebe0c1dadc5560f7e5bc0f94","tid":2213184,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T10:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5Bv-89phG9xetVSolTxJlhuYixY=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SGFABESU7VEB3BJIJPL6RGJSMU.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5Bv-89phG9xetVSolTxJlhuYixY%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSGFABESU7VEB3BJIJPL6RGJSMU.jpeg&h=378d60f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大批PTU及便衣警傍晚6時許已在知專一帶駐守。<br />\n<br />\n參與過反送中集會的15歲職訓局青年書院女生陳彥霖，去年9月底離奇赤裸浮屍海面，日前法庭召開死因聆訊，法庭曾傳召資深法醫馬宣立作供，而馬宣立則指陳彥霖的遺體被發現時全身赤裸，令他「不是很安樂」，又同意事件非常可疑及令人憂慮，令事件更顯撲朔迷離。今日（22日）網民再次於調景嶺港知專設計學院正門發起「彥霖逝世一週年悼念會」，呼籲市民到尚德十字路口或其生前就讀的調景嶺知專獻花，祭壇設有兩處蠟燭擺放區，供悼念人士擺放鮮花和蠟燭。<br />\n<br />\n大批PTU及便衣警傍晚6時許已在知專一帶駐守和巡邏，其中都會駅商場通往知專的行人天橋、知專往來調景嶺站的馬路口、及調景嶺站外，均可見警方持槍戒備。暫時未見有人聚集和獻花。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200922/HUWPPZVWKRCZNIUYHOX5GCOVHI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200922%2FHUWPPZVWKRCZNIUYHOX5GCOVHI%2F&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I27tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=f0407985\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200922%2FHUWPPZVWKRCZNIUYHOX5GCOVHI%2F&h=de858f8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200922/HUWPPZVWKRCZNIUYHOX5GCOVHI/</a>"},{"pid":"7204f2dc6b10a95d6d87d73845620a91a26987d2","tid":2213184,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T10:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"